---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-content">
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>關於我們</h4>
			<p>致力於幫您提升網路營收，從網站建置到行銷，一條龍解決方案。</p>
			<p>協助個人、企業拓展網路生意！</p>
			<div class="social-links">
				<a href="#" target="_blank">FB</a>
				<a href="#" target="_blank">IG</a>
				<a href="#" target="_blank">YT</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>公司資訊</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>地址：新北市某某區某某路123號</li>
				<li>Email: contact@example.com</li>
				<li>營業時間：09:00 - 18:00 (週一至週五)</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>相關服務</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="#">客製網頁設計</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">SEO 行銷服務</a></li>
				<li><a href="#">廣告投放服務</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-col">
			<h4>網站連結</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/about">關於我們</a></li>
				<li><a href="/blog">部落格</a></li>
				<li><a href="/contact">聯絡我們</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="copyright">
		&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Your Company Name. All rights reserved.
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		background-color: #0F0F0F; /* Very dark/black */
		color: #ccc;
		padding: 4em 1em 2em 1em;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}
	
	.footer-content {
		max-width: var(--content-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding-bottom: 3rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.footer-content {
			grid-template-columns: 2fr 1.5fr 1fr 1fr;
		}
	}

	h4 {
		color: var(--accent);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1em;
	}

	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}

	a {
		color: #ccc;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	a:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.social-links a {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 36px;
		height: 36px;
		background: #333;
		border-radius: 50%;
		color: white;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
	}
	
	.social-links a:hover {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: black;
	}

	.copyright {
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		color: #666;
		font-size: 0.85em;
	}
</style>
